
VIMDIFF CHEATSHEET
==================

LAUNCH
------
vimdiff file1 file2  Diff edit two files
:diffsplit file2     Diff file2 from inside Vim

NAVIGATION
----------
]c   Next change
[c   Previous change

COPY CHANGES BETWEEN WINDOWS
----------------------------
dp   Diff Put change into other window
do   Diff Obtain change from other window

<BREAK>

GENERAL CONCEPTS
----------------
You can edit the files using 
normal vim edit commands

FOLDING (COLLAPSED BLOCKS)
--------------------------
zo            Open fold under cursor
zO            Open fold recursively
za            Alternate fold/unfold
zR            Reveal all folds
zM            Mash down all folds

WINDOW MOVEMENT
---------------
^Ww or ^W^W   Move to other window
^W h or ^W->  Move to left window
^W l or ^W->  Move to right window
^W k          Move to upper window
^W j          Move to lower window
